passages.text:
(display:"count")

something is stuck in your head. a song from the bar, last weekend. it's the same kind of song that you would've heard decades ago at your middle school dances.

{

(live: 3.2s)[

	(set:$cycle to ($cycle + 1))
	(if: $cycle is 4)[(set:$cycle to 1)]
	(if: $cycle is 1)[(link:"you'll have to go look it up, later")[(set:$anxiety to $anxiety - 1)(goto:"Portal Portal")]]
	(if: $cycle is 2)[(link:"you can't remember the words—you just hear the melody from the chorus again and again")[(goto:"Portal Portal")]]
	(if: $cycle is 3)[(link:"your thoughts wander at the worst times, and the song sucks")[(set:$anxiety to $anxiety + 1)(goto:"Portal Portal")]]


]}

(display:"count")

the mosquito bite on your hand has almost healed. 

{

(live: 2.5s)[

	(set:$cycle to ($cycle + 1))
	(if: $cycle is 4)[(set:$cycle to 1)]
	(if: $cycle is 1)[(link:"it's a fading reminder of a nice walk")[(set:$anxiety to $anxiety - 1)(goto:"Portal Portal")]]
	(if: $cycle is 2)[(link:"you resist the urge to scratch it")[(goto:"Portal Portal")]]
	(if: $cycle is 3)[(link:"scratching it a bit can't hurt")[(set:$anxiety to $anxiety + 1)(goto:"Portal Portal")]]


]}
